title: Экспедиция Восход. Этно-хроники
overview: "Expedition Voskhod" is a union of nomadic musicians, adventurers and content creators. This is the story of their 100-day road trip across Russia in two GAZ-24 Volgas and a mobile recording studio based on a UAZ SGR. In search of the root sound, the "Expedition Voskhod" team visited the Russian North, central Russia, Dagestan, the Urals, Altai and Buryatia.
